column3: “The most gassy OG I have ever come across, such a perfumey undertone of the black water cross. Best strain of 2015”
“I didn't really like the aroma it put off. But the sensation it had: euphoria, relaxation, and a good sleep made me love it. It's dank for sure. I'll be glad to pick this up again!”

“5/5 - Michael Phelps OG 
The description here is pretty close - take a small dose and you can still function.. Take a few more hits to the dome and Indica effects start to take over.

Then I take a few more huge rips and each pull feels like diving into a pool of pine scented bubbles. Tastes like smoking pine needles - out of a pine cone, then pine tar and pine sap dripping on the exhale. Sleep follows soon after. Ma...”
“it was a great strain but i smoked so much i was in a lazy mood all the time though........ amazing strain”

“A- :

Everything about this strain I wanted to like, but ultimately the aroma had a bit too much Sour Diesel in there taking away the sharp pine fuel stink and replacing it with a more planty sweet. 

High was great, but lacked the lung expansion that comes with other, super resiny designer OGs.”

“It was cracking. The aromatic aroma mixed with that chronic citrus that went straight to the chrome. Niggas fiending for the money, but don't want to pay a loan. South side boi look who dis guy domed over an iphone. Bararatataa ThAt good shit hmu if you Tryna smoke”

“could anyone help me where i can buy the seed of this strain? 
thanks alot much appreciated 

aimhigh”
“I feel like I'm rushing threw water 👌 nice body high, intense smell”
“my apartment and car are clean.”
“Good smooth taste, very light. Got a little headed but kept my mind racing.”
“Awesome high!! Well worth 20/g 💨”
“one of the best all around strain taste like a bag of candy on the exhale and very light on the lungs on the inhale so taking a nice rip is absolutely infigurating! love this strain A+”
“Don't have too much of it but it was decent”

“The strain I purchased didn’t taste well at all, but that was probably from poor cultivation. The effects are relaxing, nice and happy high with some creativity. Helps headache! I smoke sativa all day and end up with a headache. After a couple puffs of this my headache fades. Dark taste, great high.”
“Great smoke. Prepare for an amazing ride 💯💯”
“energizing.  smooth smoke and not bad taste.  Would not recommend for anxiety or PTSD”
“Great taste, great smell, very potent.. Love this strain. Couple bongs hits and its space bound.”

“Not a bad strain, semi sweet smell but not a kick in the face type of aroma. The effects don't show their full effects immediately, so caution when having a heavy session.  The taste matches the smell, not very strong but present nontheless”

“This is one of the best strains I've ever tried.  When my buddy first held it in his hand and I gave it a whiff, I, and all others present, noted that it smelled like we imagined the man himself to smell.  When first purchasing this strain, I had a conversation with the lass selling it to me at the Unified Collective, and we both remarked that it doesn't matter how much trouble he'd gotten in when news first broke, M...”
“Love this! It deserves every one of those 22 Olympic medals. ;-) Nice, clear high. Relaxing but not really too sleepy...just mellow. Very pleasant. Glad I grabbed a quarter!”
